{"tid":2133197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"推文指港秋後算賬 美促撤學生動源4人控罪","createTime":"2020-07-31T02:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T02:17:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"44fd36d8e1d77e7aed682a2c52f0ae38cca611dc","tid":2133197,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ZZFQ6LGQBEJN36JCHBHRMOFF5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FZZFQ6LGQBEJN36JCHBHRMOFF5U%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG11xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=5cf3b0bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FZZFQ6LGQBEJN36JCHBHRMOFF5U%2F&h=8535c885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ZZFQ6LGQBEJN36JCHBHRMOFF5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n推文指港秋後算賬 美促撤學生動源4人控罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iFvRUzOdFEKbTyG5ATkFpuSny3U=/907x708/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KXE7QHQAW5O2IRJRL2XEH7XZBI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiFvRUzOdFEKbTyG5ATkFpuSny3U%3D%2F907x708%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKXE7QHQAW5O2IRJRL2XEH7XZBI.gif&h=933fe7eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會在Twitter表示關注鍾翰林被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方國家安全處人員前日首度出擊，以港版國安法當中分裂國家及煽動他人分裂國家的罪名，拘捕已解散的「學生動源」前召集人鍾翰林及三名前成員，事件即時引起人權組織和美國國會關注。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：明言整頓教育界  清除「壞蘋果」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n倡美院校與港大割席<br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會推文關注此事，指學生動源在全國人大通過港版國安法同日下午已解散，提控有秋後算賬之嫌；委員會促港府撤去四人控罪，又要求聯合國委任特別報告員調查香港現況。<br />\n<br />\n委員會又就香港大學開。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LZH8PGC9y6vu-odc9jDgpciXbug=/765x344/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MEU43HVL4IHN5OOCE5VVV4LGZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLZH8PGC9y6vu-odc9jDgpciXbug%3D%2F765x344%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMEU43HVL4IHN5OOCE5VVV4LGZQ.gif&h=0917bff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該委員會由參議員魯比奧（左圖）與眾議員麥高文（右圖）擔任主席。<br />\n<br />\n人權觀察（Human Rights Watch）。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n多間國際傳媒亦有報道「國安處首捕」一事，英國廣播公司（BBC）提到學生動源在香港雖已停止運作，但在海外成員打算成立分部；BBC引述國安處高級警司李桂華之言，說即使在國外違反港版國安法，警方亦有權調查案件。英國《標準晚報》及《每日郵報》則提及拘捕時間，剛好是港大決定解僱戴耀廷之後一天，將兩者相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"}]}